</td>
<td style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->My goal is to develop a model where more of the activities/discussion rely</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->&nbsp;</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->more on peer-to-peer learning. Because it has been shown that this is good for learning, since peers listen much more to feedback from peers.</p>
