Students have an archive of TV news clips (supplied on DVD) and are given their own research question on which they write notes before the conference. In the morning of the conference day, they discuss their questions and post their answers. In the afternoon, they discuss their answers and work towards a collaborative report compiled by a volunteer coordinator. Finally, they post their report, and they can look at the reports of other groups.

